	</p>
	<p>
		<b>Useful tools</b>&#160;&#160;
		<a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/sn-utils-tools-for-servic/jgaodbdddndbaijmcljdbglhpdhnjobg?hl=en-US" target="_blank">SNUtils Chrome Extension</a>&#160;|&#160;
		<a href="https://developer.servicenow.com/connect.do#!/share/contents/9650888_xplore_developer_toolkit?v=4.05" target="_blank">Xplore Developer Toolkit</a>&#160;|&#160;
